---
import Header from "../../components/company/CompanyHeader.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/company/CompanyFooter.astro";

const EFFECTIVE_DATE = "October 29, 2025";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Legal Protocols | ImposterX</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy and Terms of Service for ImposterX." />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#FDFBF7" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
      /* --- GLOBAL VARIABLES (Ashak Studios Theme) --- */
      :root {
        --color-bg: #FDFBF7;
        --color-text-main: #2C2420;
        --color-text-muted: #6B635E;
        
        --color-primary: #8C6A5D;
        --color-primary-dark: #6D5248;
        
        --color-card-bg: #FFFFFF;
        --color-border: #E6DFD5;
        --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(44, 36, 32, 0.05);
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        color: var(--color-text-main);
        font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      h1, h2, h3, h4 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--color-text-main);
      }

      .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

      /* --- HERO --- */
      .hero {
        padding: 100px 0 80px;
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #E6DFD5;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #F5F0E6 0%, #FDFBF7 70%);
      }
      
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        color: #1A1410;
      }

      .date-badge {
        display: inline-block; padding: 6px 16px;
        background: #EDE6D9;
        color: var(--color-primary-dark);
        font-size: 12px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        font-weight: 700;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      /* TOC */
      .toc { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 32px; }
      .toc-btn {
        padding: 10px 24px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        background: #FFFFFF;
        border: 1px solid #D6CFC5;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 13px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .toc-btn:hover {
        background: #FDFBF7;
        color: var(--color-primary);
        border-color: var(--color-primary);
      }

      /* --- LEGAL CARD --- */
      .legal-card {
        background: var(--color-card-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 60px;
        margin: 60px 0;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        scroll-margin-top: 40px;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 32px;
        margin: 0 0 24px 0;
        padding-bottom: 24px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #F0EBE3;
      }
      
      .meta-info {
        font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text-muted);
        font-style: italic; display: block; margin-top: -16px; margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      h3 { font-size: 20px; color: #4A3F39; margin: 32px 0 12px; }
      p, li { font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 16px; }
      ul { margin: 0 0 24px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
      li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
      
      a { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--color-border); font-weight: 700; }
      a:hover { color: var(--color-primary-dark); border-bottom-style: solid; }

      @media(max-width: 768px) {
        .legal-card { padding: 32px; margin: 40px 0; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 32px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <Header />

    <main>
      
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
          <span class="date-badge">Effective: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</span>
          <h1>Legal Protocols</h1>
          
          <div class="toc">
            <a class="toc-btn" href="#privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a class="toc-btn" href="#terms">Terms of Service</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="container">
        <article id="privacy" class="legal-card">
          <h2 class="section-title">Privacy Policy</h2>
          <span class="meta-info">Applies to: “ImposterX” for iOS and Android.</span>

          <h3>1) Summary</h3>
          <p>We designed ImposterX to operate without collecting or storing personal data. We do not run backend servers for user data, we do not create player accounts, and we do not retain identifiers on our systems. Gameplay preferences are stored locally on your device.</p>

          <h3>2) Data We Do <em>Not</em> Collect</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>No names, email addresses, phone numbers, or passwords</li>
            <li>No precise location data</li>
            <li>No analytics or crash profiling SDKs</li>
            <li>No retention of device identifiers by Ashak Studios</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>3) Local-Only App Data</h3>
          <p>ImposterX stores limited data locally on your device, such as language selection and UI preferences. If you uninstall the game, these local records are removed.</p>

          <h3>4) Third-Party Services</h3>
          <p>We use <strong>Google Ads (AdMob)</strong> to show interstitial ads and <strong>RevenueCat</strong> to manage purchases. These providers operate under their own terms and privacy policies. We do not combine their data with our own.</p>

          <h3>5) Advertising</h3>
          <p>ImposterX shows <strong>interstitial advertisements only during the “word generation” action</strong>. No banner or rewarded ads are used. <strong>PRO Monthly</strong> disables these ads.</p>

          <h3>6) Purchases & Subscriptions</h3>
          <p>Purchases are processed by Apple App Store or Google Play. We receive only non-personal entitlement status to unlock features.</p>

          <h3>7) Children’s Privacy</h3>
          <p>If you are under the age required by local law, please use the game with a parent or guardian.</p>

          <h3>8) Changes & Contact</h3>
          <p>Updated policies will be posted here. Questions: <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a>.</p>
        </article>

        <article id="terms" class="legal-card">
          <h2 class="section-title">Terms of Service</h2>
          <span class="meta-info">Effective Date: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</span>

          <h3>1) About These Terms</h3>
          <p>These Terms govern your use of ImposterX by Ashak Studios. By using the game, you agree to these Terms.</p>

          <h3>2) License</h3>
          <p>We grant you a personal, limited, non-exclusive license to use the game for entertainment. No reverse engineering or commercial exploitation allowed.</p>

          <h3>3) Advertising</h3>
          <p>Interstitial ads appear during word generation. <strong>PRO Monthly</strong> removes these ads while active.</p>

          <h3>4) Purchases & Subscriptions</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Processing:</strong> Handled by Apple/Google.</li>
            <li><strong>PRO Monthly:</strong> Auto-renewing subscription to remove ads.</li>
            <li><strong>Refunds:</strong> Handled under platform policies.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>5) Connectivity</h3>
          <p>Internet access is required for ads and subscription checks. Offline mode may reflect stale status.</p>

          <h3>6) Liability</h3>
          <p>The game is provided “as is.” We disclaim warranties of merchantability and fitness for a particular purpose.</p>

          <h3>7) Contact</h3>
          <p>Support: <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a></p>
        </article>
      </section>

    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>